The paper deals with algorithms for data visualization, which is a topic that falls under computer graphics (cs.GR). The paper also mentions the use of machine learning techniques (cs.AI) and efficient data structures (cs.DS) to handle large datasets. Additionally, the paper discusses the allocation of objects onto a 2D grid layout, which is a common technique in computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the paper mentions the use of optimization algorithms (cs.LG) to solve the visualization task at hand.
